Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.64,xin,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,131.667)}同上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.64,xin,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,170.667)}双臂推举
