Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:34.40,pm9,,0,0,0,,{\move(-3,333,638,333,28,5742)}你的电池呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:37.11,pm9,,0,0,0,,{\move(-18,342.667,640,342.667)}你要去哪儿
